				<h1 class="name post-title entry-title" itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing"><span itemprop="name">The US will be on a gold standard in 12 to 24 months &#8211; Schiff</span></h1>

				
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="share-post">
